@startuml real_time_feedback_sequence
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Learner" as Learner
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Scoring Service\n(Go)" as Scoring
database "Content DB" as DB

Learner -> Gateway: GET /assessment/hint?questionId=...
Gateway -> Scoring: Forward Request
activate Scoring

Scoring -> DB: GetQuestionHints(questionId)
activate DB
DB --> Scoring: Hints List
deactivate DB

Scoring -> Scoring: Select Relevant Hint
note right: Based on previous attempts\nor random selection

Scoring --> Gateway: Hint Content
deactivate Scoring
Gateway --> Learner: Display Hint

@enduml
